{"arkId":"cl010099970","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099970","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1675 - 1700 (bo\u00eetier) et 1700 - 1750 (mouvement)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1675,"endYear":1700,"imprecision":"","text":"4e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1750,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Huaud, Jean-Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1655","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1723","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Emailleur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q37766098"},{"label":"Huaud, Amy","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1657","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1724","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Emailleur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8443","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond orn\u00e9 d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne repr\u00e9sentant La Charit\u00e9 romaine d\u0027apr\u00e8s une oeuvre de Rubens grav\u00e9e par C. Van Caukercken : une jeune femme, vue de profil \u00e0 mi-corps, allaite son p\u00e8re prisonnier. Contre-\u00e9mail peint d\u0027un paysage o\u00f9 se trouve un \u00e9difice en ruines situ\u00e9 sur un promontoire rocheux, au premier plan un jeune homme joue du flageolet. Carrure orn\u00e9e de quatre m\u00e9daillons ovales repr\u00e9sentant des paysages vari\u00e9s s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des noeuds jaune dor\u00e9 sur fond bleu. Mascaron peint \u00e0 l\u0027oppos\u00e9 de la t\u00eate du pendant qui est en forme d\u0027anneau. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, points et traits indiquant les demi-heures et quarts d\u0027heure ; aiguille moulur\u00e9e ; centre du cadran orn\u00e9 d\u0027une guirlande de roses. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, quatre piliers en forme de tulipes. Balancier muni d\u0027un spiral-r\u00e9glant, rosette de r\u00e9glage encadr\u00e9e d\u0027une applique ajour\u00e9e, grav\u00e9e de rinceaux et de deux enfants. Coq circulaire \u00e0 deux oreilles reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux sym\u00e9triques, dispos\u00e9s en quatre groupes s\u00e9par\u00e9s.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; bo\u00eetier sign\u00e9 : Huaud.f","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,3","displayDimension":"5,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4,2","displayDimension":"4,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"3,9","displayDimension":"3,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2","displayDimension":"2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9